  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181230/extras/a64b31f49f4df423d9bbaef9a8579013.avif?t=1671809960\" width=576 height=144 /></span><br><br>It's finally Summer! And so you and your friends decided to go camping in the woods!  When suddenly one of your friends disappears! Embark on a short adventure story game with retro graphics, go through the forest and discover the truth behind it all.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181230/extras/6759cd0a8ed4f588b53e110a6cb10417.poster.avif?t=1671809960\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181230/extras/6759cd0a8ed4f588b53e110a6cb10417.webm?t=1671809960\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181230/extras/6759cd0a8ed4f588b53e110a6cb10417.mp4?t=1671809960\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Through the Forest</h2><br>Explore through the forest during the day, then dive deep in the darkness of the forest at night.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181230/extras/24bbf5aeab958d15a8095101ae327a0b.poster.avif?t=1671809960\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181230/extras/24bbf5aeab958d15a8095101ae327a0b.webm?t=1671809960\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181230/extras/24bbf5aeab958d15a8095101ae327a0b.mp4?t=1671809960\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Watch your back</h2><br>Run and hide, as you progress through the florest, beware what will be lurking... You never know when there'll be an animal ready to attack you...<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Be sure to gather pebbles, they'll be useful.</li></ul>",
